{
  "chapter": 59,
  "chapter_summary": "第五十九章\"老猫烧须\"承接上章，寇仲孤身挑战李子通。寇仲以长生诀先天刀气震慑对手，徐子陵在旁虎视眈眈形成威慑，两人联手以截然不同的阴阳真气配合，令李子通处处受制。激战十余招后，李子通虽以九节铜鞭重创两人，但自身也付出惨痛代价，最终主动撤退卖个人情。战后众人在船上休整，萧大姐对寇仲刮目相看，云玉真则试图招揽徐子陵。徐子陵察觉寇仲野心日增——他接近云玉真实为收服巨鲲帮的手段，与自己淡泊名利的心境渐行渐远，兄弟间由此生出微妙隔阂。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "还不去帮小仲。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 29,
      "line_end": 29
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不用怕！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_li_zi_tong",
      "text": "李子通果然有点道行，让我们再战一百回合。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zi_tong",
      "speaker_name": "李子通",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难怪老杜如此推许你们，果然有真材实料，令李某都不由生出爱才之心，此事到此作罢，祝各位顺风顺水。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zi_tong",
      "speaker_name": "李子通",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "好胆！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 135,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "打胜了！打胜了！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_da_jie",
      "speaker_name": "萧大姐",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "原来你们真是这样厉害，连李子通都给打跑了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xiao_da_jie",
      "text": "他只是知难而退吧！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_yun_yu_zhen",
      "text": "李子通怎会知道我们在船上呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 187,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "云玉真",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "玉山正在为此事盘问手下，看会是谁作内鬼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 189,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_da_jie",
      "speaker_name": "萧大姐",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "事情不会这么容易解决，以李子通的为人，尽避表面说得漂亮，说不定会暗中通知李密，好借刀杀人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "吓死人哩！小仲喷了这么多血出来。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你真的没事吗？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 197,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "真的没事。不过今晚却难替山小子疗伤了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "到你完全复元再说吧！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_da_jie",
      "speaker_name": "萧大姐",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "明早就可抵江都，希望今晚不会再出事吧！",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_yun_yu_zhen",
      "text": "我要回房睡觉了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "云玉真",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你睡觉关人家甚么事？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "让弟弟送素姐回房休息。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 213,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_da_jie",
      "speaker_name": "萧大姐",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "人家刚来，你就要去睡觉吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 215,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xiao_da_jie",
      "text": "待我服侍素姐后，大姐到小弟的卧房来谈心吧！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_da_jie",
      "speaker_name": "萧大姐",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "待本姑娘训导你这不知死活的小子，内伤最忌酒和色，我还要你去对付宇文化及，不想害你呢。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 227,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xiao_da_jie",
      "text": "大姐真坦白！",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_da_jie",
      "speaker_name": "萧大姐",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "徐公子和仲少性格很不相同呢？为何竟能相处这么融洽。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_xiao_da_jie",
      "text": "或者因自幼都在一起吧！早惯了互相迁就。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 247,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "云玉真",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你们从来不吵架吗？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 251,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_yun_yu_zhen",
      "text": "当然有吵架，不过气消了就没有事了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "云玉真",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你是否很讨厌我这美人儿师傅呢？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_yun_yu_zhen",
      "text": "若你曾给人骗过，会有甚么感受呢？那晚云帮主与独孤策鬼混和说话时，我两个正躲在一角，才决定要逃走的。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "云玉真",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "原来是这样，难怪寇仲会对我不规矩，而你却心生鄙视。不过人家也有苦衷，偌大一个帮，若没有强硬的靠山，早给人兼并了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 291
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "云玉真",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "江都事了后，我可安排你们藏身处，包保稳当。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 293,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "云玉真",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "好好的想想吧！",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 301,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_yun_yu_zhen",
      "text": "寇仲怎样对你不规矩呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "云玉真",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "他那么坏，教人家怎么说呢？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 305,
      "line_end": 306
    }
  ],
